data.name: label4.Text
data.value:
This application is used to convert a specified amount of XP to Prize Bulbs and vice-versa. To use this application, all you have to do is put in an amount of XP or Prize Bulbs, then click the "Convert" button. This app will also tell you how many Rainbow Stars can be used to purchase the set amount of Prize Bulbs, however it is currently limited to only work for 50 Prize Bulbs or less.
